    "summary": "My entrepreneurial, proactive attitude combined with my empathetic, strategic mind are the basis for my approach to work. I think unconventionally and see solutions. \n\nIt enables me to connect with people quickly and naturally build relationships.\n\nI get excited from managing and realising large-scaled, meaningful projects together with other passionate and dedicated people. I am driven by involving stakeholders to get the job done. I\nbelieve in the power of each person and the amplifier of power that networks can bring. \n\nOver the past 15 years, I set up, structured and managed several companies and teams and multiple major complex projects in Europe and Asia. \n\nTogether with amazing teams I serviced governments and global corporates (marketing, projectmanagement, creative) and international SME\u2019s (consultancy, corporate services). \n\nI enjoyed living and working in The Netherlands, China, Hong Kong, Singapore, Malaysia and Indonesia between 2005 and 2016. I am currently based in Maastricht, The Netherlands.",
